name: It Takes A Village
description:
One of the enduring qualities of growing up in a co-op is a true sense of community. Thousands upon thousands of families from different backgrounds all coming together in a shared experience. You learn to co-exist and find common ground, especially during uncommon times. Even when I return here, alone and uncertain, that sense of community and support fills my heart. You might not see anyone in this picture, but there they are, always on call during times of need.

3480x2160 JPEG

Photo by Jason Charnick
Taken in the Bronx, NY, USA
